Jean Louisa Kelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Louisa_Kelly 0 Jean Louisa Kelly (born March 9, 1972) is an American actress. After making her film debut as Tia Russell in Uncle Buck (1989) alongside John Candy, she appeared in a wide range of other films including The Fantasticks (1995) and Mr. Holland's Opus (1995). From 2000 to 2006, she was known for portraying Kim Warner on the CBS sitcom Yes, Dear. Jean_Louisa_Kelly ( born March_9_,_1972 ) is an_American_actress .
